{"tid":1488897,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[浸大?]中國和平統一促進會?","createTime":"2019-08-19T17:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T02:00:08.000Z","uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a6fcc300d207f3d7bbf1cb218b5dfa4e5c500e2c","tid":1488897,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:28:39.000Z","msg":"想問清楚浸大同學， 係唔係全部同一人？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkbu.edu.hk/tch/about/honlist/2013_hondoc_KennedyYHWong.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkbu.edu.hk%2Ftch%2Fabout%2Fhonlist%2F2013_hondoc_KennedyYHWong.jsp&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=54ab1f18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkbu.edu.hk/tch/about/honlist/2013_hondoc_KennedyYHWong.jsp</a><br />\n中國和平統一促進會香港總會 黃英豪會長 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.happrc.hk/file/publication//53fa9f17bae97.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.happrc.hk%2Ffile%2Fpublication%2F%2F53fa9f17bae97.pdf&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=12e6edf6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.happrc.hk/file/publication//53fa9f17bae97.pdf</a><br />\n「保公義撐修例大聯盟」召集人黃英豪<br />\n「守護香港」聯合召集人黃英豪<br />\n 阿爾巴尼亞共和國駐香港名譽總領事<br />\n香港民眾安全服務隊副處長<br />\n<br />\n全城集氣齊撐警 保公義撐修例大聯盟召集人黃英豪：撐警集會振奮人心！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/OcP4uT-Lf48/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FOcP4uT-Lf48%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=bae5bca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OcP4uT-Lf48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOcP4uT-Lf48&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=6058c59f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OcP4uT-Lf48</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://silentmajority.hk/articles/1003135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsilentmajority.hk%2Farticles%2F1003135&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=3ad058db\" target=\"_blank\">https://silentmajority.hk/articles/1003135</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2370000/2372246/KakaoTalk_20190609_131955951_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2370000%2F2372246%2FKakaoTalk_20190609_131955951_1024_1024.jpg&h=7ab1fa71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n控梁顯利么子 投資報喜不報憂<br />\n黃英豪輸外匯1500萬索償<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20050524/4910984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20050524%2F4910984&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=ddf47084\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20050524%2F4910984&h=b91ce2ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20050524/4910984</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://foundation.hkbu.edu.hk/sites/default/files/styles/media_gallery_large/public/pg/gallery/dr._kennedy_y.h._wong_endowed_chair_of_chinese_medicine_cum_inaugural_lecture_by_professor_lu_aiping_dean_and_foundation_endowed_chair_of_chinese_medicine/DSC_0007.JPG?itok=SSQXjB8-\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffoundation.hkbu.edu.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fmedia_gallery_large%2Fpublic%2Fpg%2Fgallery%2Fdr._kennedy_y.h._wong_endowed_chair_of_chinese_medicine_cum_inaugural_lecture_by_professor_lu_aiping_dean_and_foundation_endowed_chair_of_chinese_medicine%2FDSC_0007.JPG%3Fitok%3DSSQXjB8-&h=8160f8a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃博士與香港浸會大學關係密切，淵源很深。<br />\n<br />\n政協黃英豪涉賄案 錢大康曾志偉擔品格證人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2621771-%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E9%BB%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%B1%AA%E6%B6%89%E8%B3%84%E6%A1%88-%E9%8C%A2%E5%A4%A7%E5%BA%B7%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E6%93%94%E5%93%81%E6%A0%BC%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2621771-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2594%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25B3%2584%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589%25E6%2593%2594%25E5%2593%2581%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=81b637a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2621771-%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E9%BB%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%B1%AA%E6%B6%89%E8%B3%84%E6%A1%88-%E9%8C%A2%E5%A4%A7%E5%BA%B7%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E6%93%94%E5%93%81%E6%A0%BC%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%BA</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2015/05/20150520_CR_%E9%8C%A2%E5%A4%A7%E5%BA%B7_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2015%2F05%2F20150520_CR_%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BA%25B7_1.jpg&h=3b0696a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/11/20171112_EN_%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89_%E6%88%91%E6%84%9BEYT_FB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F11%2F20171112_EN_%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589_%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2584%259BEYT_FB.jpg&h=c8ac124d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n律師黃英豪被指拖欠8700萬元 被海外公司入稟追討<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/290165/%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E9%BB%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%B1%AA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%8B%96%E6%AC%A08700%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E8%A2%AB%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E8%BF%BD%E8%A8%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F290165%2F%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258B%2596%25E6%25AC%25A08700%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25A8%259F%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A8%258E&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=c3217169\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/290165/%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E9%BB%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%B1%AA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%8B%96%E6%AC%A08700%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E8%A2%AB%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E8%BF%BD%E8%A8%8E</a><br />\n<br />\n黃英豪涉行賄表證成立<br />\n【本報訊】全國政協委員兼上市公司香港資源前主席黃英豪（54歲，圖）涉貪案昨在區院續審，黃被裁定表證成立，他選擇不出庭自辯，亦不傳召證人。<br />\n不過，黃呈上19封包括基本法委員會副主任梁愛詩、警務處前處長鄧竟成、立法會議員梁美芬、無綫前行政主席梁乃鵬、港區人大代表鄭耀棠等人撰寫的品格證明信，以及黃的捐款收據。案件押後至本月27日進行結案陳詞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171114/20213741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F20213741&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=01275443\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F20213741&h=5d32dfac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171114/20213741</a><br />\n<br />\n全國政協委員兼上市公司前主席黃英豪，涉於2007年上巿公司海域化工集團有限公司上巿時，行賄該上巿公司前董事許浩明案，控辯雙方早前完成結案陳詞，法官今裁決被告脫罪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/05/18/153646/i_640x377_000534815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F05%2F18%2F153646%2Fi_640x377_000534815.jpg&h=755859ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全国政协委员黄英豪等人涉嫌行贿，被香港廉政公署起诉<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1359471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thepaper.cn%2FnewsDetail_forward_1359471&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=8cad0773\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1359471</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://image.thepaper.cn/www/image/4/484/551.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.thepaper.cn%2Fwww%2Fimage%2F4%2F484%2F551.jpg&h=06919688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港廉政公署起诉3人涉贿 全国政协委员黄英豪涉案<br />\n<a href=\"http://finance.ifeng.com/a/20150802/13883511_0.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.ifeng.com%2Fa%2F20150802%2F13883511_0.shtml&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=3dafee06\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.ifeng.com/a/20150802/13883511_0.shtml</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://y1.ifengimg.com/cmpp/2015/08/02/12/8801fa7a-337f-45fd-99c0-0045a5298604_size82_w419_h550.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fy1.ifengimg.com%2Fcmpp%2F2015%2F08%2F02%2F12%2F8801fa7a-337f-45fd-99c0-0045a5298604_size82_w419_h550.jpg&h=4fbebb6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃英豪被指行賄案 獲裁定脫罪<br />\n被告黃英豪（54歲）被指於2009年8月19日向許提供利益，即以180萬元認購1,500萬股香港資源控股（前稱海域化工）優先股的1港元認股權，作為許建議香港資源收購金至尊珠寶等事宜的報酬等。<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1985365/%E9%BB%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%B1%AA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%A1%8C%E8%B3%84%E6%A1%88%E3%80%80%E7%8D%B2%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1985365%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25B3%2584%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%258D%25B2%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259A%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=b70e42aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1985365/%E9%BB%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%B1%AA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%A1%8C%E8%B3%84%E6%A1%88%E3%80%80%E7%8D%B2%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恭喜成功脫罪</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同一人定係撞樣?</span></span>"},{"pid":"b4eb33b52fed533ac775a26763f5e5d690b9758e","tid":